com.nokia.maps.kml

Interface Icon


  • public interface Icon
    This interface represents the <Icon> tag from KML specification.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static java.lang.String ELEMENT
      This constant indicates the <Icon> XML element.
      static java.lang.String HREF
      This constant defines "href" as an XML attribute.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      java.lang.String getHref()
      This method retrieves an HTTP address or a local file specification used to load an icon.
      javax.microedition.lcdui.Image getImage()
      This method retrieves an image to use as an icon.

    • Field Detail

      • ELEMENT

        static final java.lang.String ELEMENT
        This constant indicates the <Icon> XML element.

      • HREF

        static final java.lang.String HREF
        This constant defines "href" as an XML attribute. The href attribute is used when associating an image to this <Icon>.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
